WEBVTT

00:02.500 --> 00:04.216
<i>Previously on Mistresses... </i>

00:04.245 --> 00:06.879
Some trash showed up at my doorstep
with my cheating ex-husband's

00:06.916 --> 00:08.156
bi-ratial spun.

00:08.180 --> 00:10.157
Then why do I feel like
I'm doing something wrong?

00:10.182 --> 00:11.815
Keeping Paul away from Lucy?

00:11.855 --> 00:13.387
It's over. Paul's dead.

00:13.432 --> 00:14.808
<i>The body has</i>
<i>now since confirmed</i>

00:14.808 --> 00:16.372
<i>to be that of Paul Malloy,</i>

00:16.400 --> 00:19.101
<i>who was previously thought</i>
<i>to have died years ago.</i>

00:19.136 --> 00:21.992
A man I slept with just
tested H.I.V. positive.

00:22.017 --> 00:23.116
Oh, my God.

00:23.141 --> 00:25.741
I'm not sure if I believe in God anymore.

00:25.766 --> 00:28.751
Is it positive or negative?
Just tell me the damn results.

00:29.046 --> 00:31.113
You want to marry me today?

00:31.148 --> 00:32.848
Yeah. I do.

00:32.883 --> 00:35.032
- You are freakishly happy.
- [Chuckles]

00:35.057 --> 00:36.467
You have a secret.

00:40.024 --> 00:41.835
Harry: I am crazy in love with you,

00:41.860 --> 00:44.303
and I don't know what to do
because I know that it can't be.

00:44.328 --> 00:45.394
Stop.

